data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT!!  A single family home UNDER $500,000 in MILLCREEK?!?!  Shut the Front Door!  Welcome to this beautiful 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom bungalow nestled in the heart of Millcreek, Utah. This inviting home combines classic charm with modern updates, offering the perfect blend of comfort and style.  Enjoy easy access to local parks, shopping centers, dining options, and excellent schools in the SLC School District.   Highlighted features:  Cozy kitchen with stainless steel appliances  Updated bathroom  Hardwood floors, lots of natural light and that Bungalow Charm   Private backyard oasis, ideal for outdoor gatherings  Attached 1 car garage   New siding installed 2021  Don't miss the opportunity to make this delightful bungalow your forever home. Come see for yourself and experience the warmth and comfort of this charming property.   Square footage figures are provided as a courtesy estimate only and were obtained from County Records.  Buyer is advised to obtain an independent measurement.
